ion systems and, with the help of the\ntechniques of first return maps, for all aforementioned conformal dynamical\nsystems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 May 2016 07:21:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 7 Oct 2017 11:35:36 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 22 Jun 2018 08:44:26 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 2 Jan 2019 14:01:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-03"}
