utions can be used to solve the FRG-flow equation for the\ntwo-particle GF (in particular, the relationship between the regulators in the\ntwo methods) is studied.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 May 2016 13:15:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-25"}
